snippet.title: SAVIOR OF THE ABYSS | Full Game Playthrough | Steam Game | All Endings
snippet.description:
Savior of the Abyss is a horror RPG-maker game about a girl whose mission is to escape the facility. With many monsters lurking in the corners, will she be able to do so?

SOME TIPS:
- Being so curious about things will lead you to death in this game. Just save your every progress.

SP: You'll see some lag in this video - that is because my PC is old. I hope you'll understand. Thank you!

***********
